## Offer Schemas by Product Type

The `details` object in each offer is typed by `product_type`. The schemas for each type are defined as named references below and will be documented in full separately.

| `product_type`    | `details` Schema Reference      |
|-------------------|---------------------------------|
| `credit_cards`    | `CreditCardProductDetails`      |
| `personal_loans`  | `LoanProductDetails`            |
| `student_loans`   | `LoanProductDetails`            |
| `auto_loans`      | `LoanProductDetails`            |
| `auto_insurance`  | `InsuranceProductDetails`       |
| `home_insurance`  | `InsuranceProductDetails`       |
| `mortgage`        | `MortgageProductDetails`        |
| `home_equity`     | `HomeEquityProductDetails`      |
| `savings`         | `WealthProductDetails`          |
| `checking`        | `WealthProductDetails`          |
| `mma`             | `WealthProductDetails`          |
| `cds`             | `WealthProductDetails`          |

**Example offer object:**

```json
{
  "offer_id": "off_6092",
  "product_type": "credit_cards",
  "details": { "$ref": "CreditCardProductDetails" }
}
```

