## Data Model

### `profiles` Table

| Column               | DB Type        | Nullable | Notes                                        |
|----------------------|----------------|----------|----------------------------------------------|
| `id`                 | UUID (PK)      | No       | Internal primary key, auto-generated.        |
| `master_customer_id` | VARCHAR(255)   | No       | Partner-supplied ID. Unique index.           |
| `email`              | VARCHAR(320)   | No       | Indexed for lookups.                         |
| `first_name`         | VARCHAR(255)   | Yes      |                                              |
| `last_name`          | VARCHAR(255)   | Yes      |                                              |
| `home_address`       | TEXT           | No       |                                              |
| `zip_code`           | CHAR(5)        | No       | Indexed.                                     |
| `credit_score_band`  | VARCHAR(20)    | No       | Constrained to enum values.                  |
| `annual_income`      | DECIMAL(15, 2) | Yes      |                                              |
| `is_student`         | BOOLEAN        | Yes      |                                              |
| `last_4_ssn`         | VARCHAR(255)   | Yes      | Stored encrypted at rest.                    |
| `source_file`        | VARCHAR(500)   | No       | Name of the CSV file this record came from.  |
| `ingested_at`        | TIMESTAMPTZ    | No       | Set on insert.                               |
| `updated_at`         | TIMESTAMPTZ    | No       | Updated on each upsert.                      |

